(=PAGE
TITLE=>Upload Picture

BODY<=

(=H1 Upload your Picture H1=)
(=P
Here you can upload a miniature picture that will be used to represent you through the LiveJournal site, in your journal, and in your friends' journals.  The following restrictions are placed on the file:
<UL>
<LI>File size must be less than 40k
<LI>Image dimensions must be no larger than 100x100 pixels
<LI>File format must be either PNG, GIF or JPG
</UL>
P=)

<FORM ACTION="uploadpic_do.bml" METHOD="POST" ENCTYPE="multipart/form-data">

(=STANDOUT
<TABLE>
(=_CODE
 require 'ljlib.pl'; 
 return &auth_fields();
 _CODE=)
